descriptionNullable:
### Context
Novel Corona Virus (COVID-19) epidemiological data since 22 January 2020.  The number of new cases are increasing day by day around the world. Fields available in the data include Country/Region, Reported new daily new cases, tests, deaths, vaccination status and smoothed data for India. The data is compiled by the Johns Hopkins University Center for Systems Science and Engineering (JHU CCSE) from various sources including the World Health Organization (WHO), DXY.cn, BNO News, Our World in Data, National Health Commission of the People’s Republic of China (NHC), China CDC (CCDC), Hong Kong Department of Health, Macau Government, Taiwan CDC, US CDC and Government of India.

### Acknowledgements
The dataset was obtained from the publicly available information, I do not own any information.
